latestIgtvVideos.title: Purva Turns 18🌝
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Happiest Birthday to you my heart🙈💕I don't know what you write tbh I don't have words😢All the time spent with you has been amazing and I can't thank you enough for everything💙This 5 year journey with you has been a roller coaster of happiness and fun😻I just laugh when I m with you and I best part is I never regret all the stupidity done with you😂From bunking lectures to long drives each moment spent is worth it😍Thankyou for always being my story listener,my pj partner,my twinnie,my sukh dukh ki saath and lot more😂I day dosen't end if I don't shout at you,u know I love you right😋🌝I have seen you grow mature and I know you right from you were a kid who always took the worst decisions ever😜I have always been there and I will be there whenever you want me and you don't even need to say🙊I may shout but that's why I love you the most haan😘😜
Cheers to all the memories we have made and will continue making😍
Happy 18th my bitch🌏❤
Love you loads and loads🙈💙

Wholesome moments from 2025:

1. First day at office, finally offline!
2. Discovered a new favorite recipe I whipped up myself
3. Breathtaking sunset at Marine Drive
4. Heartwarming moment: Nani painting her granddaughter’s nails
5. Had a blast doing Massi’s makeup and clicking pics together
6.First cousin to get engaged: we danced like anything
7. Scored amazing jewelry finds in Colaba
8. Cherished a rare, empty local train ride
9. Celebrated Aayushi’s special day - she looked stunning!
10. Bombay’s hidden gems: adorable stray cats (spotted on a post-lunch walk)
